::Striker::

Striker shakes his head, the pod shaking with the storm outside. "We've been 
pressed for resources lately. Before the Cybertronian Fire crashed with loads 
of energon. There's no spare energon here."

He looks around the pod, and then at Spears. "The storm is going to mess with 
the energy collection by the solar panels. We-"

A quake goes through the pod, nearly throwing Striker out of his seat as the 
storm passes over the pod, the pod's lights flickering.
